# Admin UI

## Structure

- `MyAdminIndexView` — `/`, `/login/`, `/logout/`
- `BookingAdmin` — Reservas (main CRUD + custom actions)
- `UserView` — Preferencias (notification/sync flags only)
- `EventView` — hidden read-only audit log

## Access control

- `is_accessible()` requires Flask-Login.
- All queries scoped to `login.current_user.id`.
- Max 30 bookings per user.

## Custom endpoints (BookingAdmin)

- `POST .../active` — toggle `is_active` + start/stop Booker
- `POST .../sync-wodbuster-bookings`
- `POST .../cancel-wodbuster-booking`

## Templates

- Custom list/edit under `wodbooker/templates/admin/booking/`
- Base: `wodbooker/templates/base.html` (Bootstrap 4)

## i18n

- Flask-Babel; default locale `es`; `?lang=` stored in session.

## New UI fields

1. `BookingForm` / `UserForm` in `views.py`
2. Template if not auto-rendered
3. If persisted → model + migration (skill `db-migration`)
